smother
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a suffocation of sheep, usually en masse [ when driven hard downhill or near water, or worried in a paddock by a dog and being forced together into a tight pack. ]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
